---
---

<figure class="my-8 not-prose">
  <svg
    viewBox="0 0 560 460"
    class="w-full h-auto"
    role="img"
    aria-label="The Prodect workflow: a pre-plan phase with an iteration loop between user and Prodect, producing a comet-shaped plan tree, followed by a build-phase execution loop where coding agents ship subtasks, and progressive expansion of the tree."
  >
    <defs>
      <marker id="pArrow" viewBox="0 0 10 10" refX="9" refY="5" markerWidth="6" markerHeight="6" orient="auto">
        <path d="M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 z" fill="#0a0a0a" />
      </marker>
      <marker id="pArrowBrand" viewBox="0 0 10 10" refX="9" refY="5" markerWidth="6" markerHeight="6" orient="auto">
        <path d="M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 z" fill="#360eff" />
      </marker>
    </defs>

    <!-- Phase label: PRE-PLAN -->
    <text x="0" y="14" font-family="Inter, sans-serif" font-size="10" font-weight="600" fill="#6b6862" letter-spacing="1.5">
      PRE-PLAN PHASE
    </text>
    <line x1="120" y1="10" x2="560" y2="10" stroke="#6b6862" stroke-width="0.5" stroke-dasharray="2 3" />

    <!-- Step 1: Describe intent -->
    <rect x="20" y="30" width="140" height="46" rx="6" fill="none" stroke="#0a0a0a" stroke-width="1.2" />
    <text x="90" y="52" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Inter, sans-serif" font-size="11" fill="#0a0a0a" font-weight="600">1. Describe intent</text>
    <text x="90" y="68" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Inter, sans-serif" font-size="10" fill="#6b6862">chat box</text>

    <path d="M160 53 L200 53" stroke="#0a0a0a" stroke-width="1.2" fill="none" marker-end="url(#pArrow)" />

    <!-- Step 2: Drafts docs -->
    <rect x="200" y="30" width="160" height="46" rx="6" fill="none" stroke="#0a0a0a" stroke-width="1.2" />
    <text x="280" y="52" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Inter, sans-serif" font-size="11" fill="#0a0a0a" font-weight="600">2. Prodect drafts</text>
    <text x="280" y="68" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Inter, sans-serif" font-size="10" fill="#6b6862">intent docs</text>

    <path d="M280 76 L280 98" stroke="#0a0a0a" stroke-width="1.2" fill="none" marker-end="url(#pArrow)" />

    <!-- Iteration loop -->
    <rect x="160" y="100" width="240" height="76" rx="8" fill="#ece8ff" stroke="#360eff" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4 3" />
    <text x="280" y="120" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Inter, sans-serif" font-size="10" font-weight="600" fill="#360eff" letter-spacing="1">
      ITERATION LOOP
    </text>
    <text x="280" y="140" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Inter, sans-serif" font-size="11" fill="#0a0a0a">
      user reads & reacts
    </text>
    <text x="280" y="156" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Inter, sans-serif" font-size="11" fill="#0a0a0a">
      ↕ Prodect revises
    </text>
    <text x="280" y="170" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Inter, sans-serif" font-size="9" fill="#6b6862" font-style="italic">
      loops until user exits
    </text>

    <path d="M280 176 L280 198" stroke="#0a0a0a" stroke-width="1.2" fill="none" marker-end="url(#pArrow)" />

    <!-- Comet-shaped plan tree -->
    <rect x="140" y="200" width="280" height="60" rx="6" fill="none" stroke="#0a0a0a" stroke-width="1.2" />
    <text x="280" y="222" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Inter, sans-serif" font-size="11" fill="#0a0a0a" font-weight="600">
      Comet-shaped plan tree
    </text>
    <text x="280" y="240" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Inter, sans-serif" font-size="10" fill="#6b6862">
      all Epics sketched · early Stories detailed
    </text>
    <text x="280" y="254" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Inter, sans-serif" font-size="10" fill="#6b6862">
      first Subtasks ready to ship
    </text>

    <path d="M280 260 L280 286" stroke="#0a0a0a" stroke-width="1.2" fill="none" marker-end="url(#pArrow)" />

    <!-- Phase label: BUILD -->
    <text x="0" y="284" font-family="Inter, sans-serif" font-size="10" font-weight="600" fill="#6b6862" letter-spacing="1.5">
      BUILD PHASE
    </text>
    <line x1="100" y1="280" x2="560" y2="280" stroke="#6b6862" stroke-width="0.5" stroke-dasharray="2 3" />

    <!-- Execution loop -->
    <rect x="100" y="290" width="360" height="120" rx="8" fill="#360eff" />
    <text x="280" y="312" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Inter, sans-serif" font-size="10" font-weight="600" fill="white" letter-spacing="1">
      EXECUTION LOOP · per Subtask
    </text>

    <rect x="120" y="324" width="100" height="34" rx="4" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="1" />
    <text x="170" y="345" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Inter, sans-serif" font-size="10" fill="white">pick Subtask</text>

    <rect x="240" y="324" width="100" height="34" rx="4" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="1" />
    <text x="290" y="340" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Inter, sans-serif" font-size="10" fill="white">deliver prompt</text>
    <text x="290" y="352" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Inter, sans-serif" font-size="9" fill="#ece8ff">to coding agent</text>

    <rect x="360" y="324" width="100" height="34" rx="4" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="1" />
    <text x="410" y="340" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Inter, sans-serif" font-size="10" fill="white">PR · review</text>
    <text x="410" y="352" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Inter, sans-serif" font-size="9" fill="#ece8ff">merge</text>

    <path d="M220 341 L240 341" stroke="white" stroke-width="1" fill="none" marker-end="url(#pArrowBrand)" />
    <path d="M340 341 L360 341" stroke="white" stroke-width="1" fill="none" marker-end="url(#pArrowBrand)" />

    <!-- Loop-back arrow -->
    <path d="M410 358 Q410 390 170 390 L170 358" stroke="white" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="3 3" fill="none" />
    <text x="280" y="402" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Inter, sans-serif" font-size="9" fill="#ece8ff" font-style="italic">
      next Subtask
    </text>

    <path d="M280 410 L280 426" stroke="#0a0a0a" stroke-width="1.2" fill="none" marker-end="url(#pArrow)" />

    <!-- Progressive expansion -->
    <rect x="140" y="428" width="280" height="28" rx="6" fill="none" stroke="#0a0a0a" stroke-width="1.2" stroke-dasharray="3 3" />
    <text x="280" y="447" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Inter, sans-serif" font-size="10" fill="#0a0a0a">
      Progressive expansion — "Plan next Story?"
    </text>
  </svg>
  <figcaption class="mt-3 text-[12px] text-[var(--color-muted)] leading-[1.5]">
    <span class="text-[var(--color-ink)]">Two phases, two loops.</span>
    The plan tree is comet-shaped — sketched at the head, detailed where work is happening next. Coding agents take the
    rich-prompt Subtasks; humans take the rest.
  </figcaption>
</figure>
